### ============================================================
### auth.rest — Authentication endpoints
### ============================================================

### ---- Variables (change host/port here to switch environments) ----
@host = localhost
@port = 3000
@baseAPI = http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api

### ============================================================
### AUTHENTICATION - POST /api/auth/...
### ============================================================

###
### Register New User
### @name authRegister
POST {{baseAPI}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "nombre": "Test User"
}

###
### Login User
### @name authLogin
POST {{baseAPI}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###
### Login - Wrong Password (Error 401)
### @name authLoginError
POST {{baseAPI}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}
